icProfile?language=EN>Orcbane</A></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>w4nn4b3!</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#000033>4/13/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#000033>9:56:50 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">LOH - now an uber taunt</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">I noticed something in the plane of air recently.  Everytime I used LOH all the mobs in the area turned on me and dropped me like a bad habit.  Guess I'll no longer be using it on myself on the uber raids.<br>
