Again, this is a tactic that I've read works on a few of the Velious mobs and since I'm still hovering at 52 for a brief time, I can't quite try it out yet.  Then again, this info may be totally inaccurate; however, the ability to DA-tank even 2 rounds of damage from a 400+ average triple attack mob could be a useful tactic in a few select encounters.</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#E5E5E6><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/uorcbane.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Orcbane</A></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>w4nn4b3!</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#000033>4/16/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#000033>5:16:15 pm</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: LOH - now an uber taunt</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">You may have missed my point, Otter.<br>
