</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#D5D4D5><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/uotterantilles.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Otter Antilles</A></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>l33t d00d!</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#000033>4/25/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#000033>10:25:45 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: LOH - now an uber taunt</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Good points, Filan.<br>
